                "id": "rule_1",
                "type": "rule",
                "content": {
                  "text": "The Antimetal Agent is a sophisticated Kubernetes controller written in Go that connects infrastructure to the Antimetal platform for cloud resource management. It's designed as a cloud-native agent that:",
